data.description: Experience spacious living with this remarkable home, thoughtfully planned with an open concept for maximum use and connectivity. The living area effortlessly flows into the dining space and kitchen, forming the perfect backdrop for entertaining and family gatherings. This home has four generously sized bedrooms, along with an inviting upstairs den. This versatile space can easily transform into a home office, a vibrant playroom, an immersive gaming sanctuary, or simply your own personal haven for relaxation. The primary bedroom is located downstairs while the other bedrooms are upstairs.  The primary bathroom is a haven of luxury, featuring a lavish bath, separate shower, double vanity, and an expansive walk-in closet that ensures your belongings have a place of their own. Step outside into a fully fenced backyard where you can unwind on the patio. Escape the summer heat by indulging in the community pool, just a leisurely stroll away from your front door, promising refreshing relaxation and delightful recreation. This home has brand new carpet too! 2023-11-21
